Sketch Hero is my first Unity Android game project that I published to Google Play store which I worked for around a year.
I spent a lot of time developing this game and I&rsquo;m really satisfied with how it turned out. I made this game to see how well I know about Unity. Sketch Hero is an endless runner, which means the player plays the game endlessly while trying to achieve the highest score possible.
